      "writtenOn": "2020-06-19T12:08:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Would it be simpler to search for both inputs and just set the value on both (instead of needing to do the type\u003d selector)? IIRC, setting the value would not trigger an input event, so it shouldn\u0027t trigger an infinite cycle.",
