      "writtenOn": "2020-06-19T21:01:57Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think only updating what needs updating is probably easier for the reader to understand.\n\nUpdating both might lead the reader to think there\u0027s an underlying reason for that, other than the programmer\u0027s convenience at the time of writing this code.",
